subject: An international QS version of "Through The Looking-Glass"
msgSnippet: Hello all, I ve uploaded Lewis Carroll s book Through The Looking-Glass re-written using my international QS proposal rules. The book is in the files/text
messageBody:
Hello all,
I've uploaded Lewis Carroll's book "Through The Looking-Glass" re-written using my international QS proposal rules.
The book is in the files/text folder.
My intQS project rules are found in the files/International Quikscript/Malt's International Quikscript Project/AAA-Intro and Notes.pdf file.

Would welcome feedback on how readable you find the text- especially across accents.
